INSERT INTO app_info_cache (app_id, app_name, category, desktop_file, cached_at)
        VALUES (?1, ?2, ?3, ?4, ?5)
        ON CONFLICT (app_id) 
        DO UPDATE SET 
            app_name = excluded.app_name,
            category = excluded.category,
            desktop_file = excluded.desktop_file,
            cached_at = excluded.cached_at
